		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />With your adapter, could it be made possible to display 960 lines in the 1080 HD mode?  This would give top and bottom borders but eliminate stretching artifacts and uneven scanlines.  Also, while you cannot obtain an 8/7 pixel aspect ratio with integer scaling, is it possible to do a pixel-perfect 1/1 and a 5/4 pixel aspect ratio within the screen resolution with the adapter?

		

		</td>
